m/JeffGrubb?ref_src=twsrc^tfw\">@JeffGrubb</a>. <a href=\"https://t.co/v8rU2N76Ak\">https://t.co/v8rU2N76Ak</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/j6jCzM5I1c\">pic.twitter.com/j6jCzM5I1c</a></p> — Jordan Middler (@JordanMiddler) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/JordanMiddler/status/1634315953176444930?ref_src=twsrc^tfw\">March 10, 2023</a></blockquote> <text></text> </div><div data-embed-type=\"tweet\" data-src=\"https://twitter.com/TMobile/status/1634306625866457114\" data-has-image=\"false\"><blockquote align=\"center\" class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-conversation=\"none\" data-mce-disable-toolbar=\"true\"><p dir=\"ltr\">Tie between Yoshi's Island and 6 Golden Coins. So many memories between those.</p> — T-Mobile (@TMobile) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/TMobile/status/1634306625866457114?ref_src=twsrc^tfw\">March 10, 2023</a></blockquote> <text></text> </div><div data-embed-type=\"tweet\" data-src=\"https://twitter.com/_janjerome/status/1633584854431563776\" data-has-image=\"true\"><blockquote align=\"center\" class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-conversation=\"none\" data-mce-disable-toolbar=\"true\"><p dir=\"ltr\">Started feeling a bit better but I think I'm gonna crawl back into my COVID cave now... <a href=\"https://t.co/iGANPbezRh\">pic.twitter.com/iGANPbezRh</a></p> — Jan Ochoa (@_janjerome) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/_janjerome/status/1633584854431563776?ref_src=twsrc^tfw\">March 8, 2023</a></blockquote> <text></text> </div><h2>Art</h2><p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/carlogocarlo/status/1634112506355482627\"><strong>Dan Cooking Show</strong></a> (By: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/carlogocarlo\">@carlogocarlo</a>)</p><p data-right-indent=\"0\" style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">Should Dan have a cooking show on the site? That has been at the heart of many debates on the community Discord as well as on social media. Over on Twitter, carlogocarlo tried to imagine, and successfully I might add, what would happen on the first episode of a Dan-led cooking show.</p><figure data-align=\"center\" data-size=\"large\" data-img-src=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3453268-0172630692-Fq2If58XsAAlOoi.jpg\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3453268\" data-ratio=\"2.2443324937028\" data-width=\"794\" data-embed-type=\"image\" style=\"width: 794px\"><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3453268-0172630692-Fq2If58XsAAlOoi.jpg\"><img alt=\"No Caption Provided\" src=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3453268-0172630692-Fq2If58XsAAlOoi.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3453268-0172630692-Fq2If58XsAAlOoi.jpg 794w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/0/8273/3453268-0172630692-Fq2If58XsAAlOoi.jpg 427w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 794px) 100vw, 794px\" data-width=\"794\"></a></figure><p><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/forums/general-discussion-30/chat-emoticon-guide-1471098/\"><strong>Egg Dan Emote</strong></a> (By: Jan)</p><p data-right-indent=\"0\" style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">Big ups to Jan coming back from COVID to grace us with one of the most hilarious emotes in a good long while! Dan might hate eggs, but this chat emoticon just works on so many levels.</p><figure data-align=\"center\" data-size=\"large\" data-img-src=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3453267-big_degg.png\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3453267\" data-ratio=\"1.5671232876712\" data-width=\"365\" data-embed-type=\"image\" style=\"width: 365px\"><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3453267-big_degg.png\"><img alt=\"No Caption Provided\" src=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3453267-big_degg.png\" srcset=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3453267-big_degg.png 365w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 365px) 100vw, 365px\" data-width=\"365\"></a></figure><h2>Activities</h2><p><strong><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/somerville/3030-82989/forums/somerville-is-the-5th-selection-of-uugpgc-year-2-f-1910092/\">Somerville Is The 5th Selection Of UUGPGC Year