ww.giantbomb.com/profile/unclejam23/\">@unclejam23</a>)</p><p data-right-indent=\"0\" style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">The first cycle of the 2023 edition of the community Album Club has reached its conclusion! The topic this time is Sorceress by Opeth! If you want to discuss the tracks on this album or learn what the plans for the group are in the future, click the link!</p><h2>Blogs</h2><p><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/fist-forged-in-shadow-torch/3030-72423/forums/indie-game-of-the-week-310-fist-forged-in-shadow-t-1910304/\"><strong>Indie Game of the Week 310: F.I.S.T.: Forged in Shadow Torch</strong></a> (By: <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/profile/mento/\">@mento</a>)</p><figure data-align=\"right\" data-size=\"small\" data-img-src=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3453276-0647219881-Fq83KpZaIAAn4RG.jpg\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3453276\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-width=\"1920\" data-embed-type=\"image\" style=\"width: 1920px\"><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3453276-0647219881-Fq83KpZaIAAn4RG.jpg\"><img alt=\"Blade Runner meets furries?\" src=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_small/0/8273/3453276-0647219881-Fq83KpZaIAAn4RG.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3453276-0647219881-Fq83KpZaIAAn4RG.jpg 1920w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_super/0/8273/3453276-0647219881-Fq83KpZaIAAn4RG.jpg 960w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/0/8273/3453276-0647219881-Fq83KpZaIAAn4RG.jpg 480w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_small/0/8273/3453276-0647219881-Fq83KpZaIAAn4RG.jpg 320w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 320px) 100vw, 320px\" data-width=\"320\"></a><figcaption>Blade Runner meets furries?</figcaption></figure><p data-right-indent=\"0\" style=\"margin-left: 30px;\"><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/fist-forged-in-shadow-torch/3030-72423/\">F.I.S.T.: Forged In Shadow Torch</a> is the topic of Mento's latest \"Indie Game of the Week\" blog! Is there more to