ills.</figcaption></figure><p data-right-indent=\"0\" style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">borgmaster has another fun PS1 retrospective blog on the site and this one looks at <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/wing-commander-iii-heart-of-the-tiger/3030-18483/\">Wing Commander III: Heart of the Tiger</a>, <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/road-track-presents-the-need-for-speed/3030-4703/\">Road &amp; Track presents The Need for Speed</a>, <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/extreme-pinball/3030-14033/\">Extreme Pinball</a>, and <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/resident-evil/3030-5842/\">Resident Evil</a>!</p><p><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/profile/purpleshyguy/blog/reconnecting-with-halo/269615/\"><strong>Reconnecting with Halo</strong></a> (By: <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/profile/purpleshyguy/\">@purpleshyguy</a>)</p><p data-right-indent=\"0\" style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">Things have not been \"great\" for the Halo franchise, but PurpleShyGuy talks about their recent attempt to get reinvested into the series. Read why <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/halo-infinite/3030-68906/\">Halo Infinite</a>'s multiplayer alone has them at least partially on board for the future!</p><p><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/turbografx-16/3045-55/forums/hucartography-vi-r-type-1910260/\"><strong>HuCARTography VI: R-Type</strong></a> (By: <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/profile/jeffrud/\">@jeffrud</a>)</p><figure data-align=\"right\" data-size=\"small\" data-img-src=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3453278-8887734365-27124.png\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3453278\" data-ratio=\"0.7510460251046\" data-width=\"956\" data-embed-type=\"image\" style=\"width: 956px\"><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3453278-8887734365-27124.png\"><img alt=\"Real talk, I always had a hard time with the third boss of R-Type; the military battlecruiser.\" src=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_small/0/8273/3453278-8887734365-27124.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3453278-8887734365-27124.png 956w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/0/8273/3453278-8887734365-27124.jpg 480w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_small/0/8273/3453278-8887734365-27124.jpg 320w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 320px) 100vw, 320px\" data-width=\"320\"></a><figcaption>Real talk, I always had a hard time with the third boss of R-Type; the military battlecruiser.</figcaption></figure><p data-right-indent=\"0\" style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">It's time to talk about a gaming CLASSIC with JeffRud's latest HuCARTography blog which this time looks at the catalog of games on the TurboGrafx-16, or PC Engine with a write-up on <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/r-type/3030-13745/\">R-Type</a>!</p><p><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/profile/gamer_152/blog/move-on-up-possessions-in-unpacking/269557/\"><strong>Move On Up: Possessions in Unpacking</strong></a> (By: <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/profile/gamer_152/\">@gamer_152</a>)</p><p data-right-indent=\"0\" style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">Unpacking by <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/witch-beam/3010-9133/\">Witch Beam</a> appears to have a simple premise: You characterize a home through belongings, but the number of places it manages to take that premise is mind-blowing.</p><h2>Discussion Threads</h2><p><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/suicide-squad-kill-the-justice-league/3030-80097/forums/suicide-squad-delayed-again-1910276/\"><strong>Suicide Squad Delayed Again</strong></a> (By: <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/profile/av_gamer/\">@av_gamer</a>)</p><figure data-align=\"right\" data-size=\"small\" data-img-src=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3453182-9067400311-Fq3tRS1aYAIXn-j.jpg\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3453182\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-width=\"2048\" data-embed-type=\"image\" style=\"width: 2048px\"><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3453182-9067400311-Fq3tRS1aYAIXn-j.jpg\"><img alt=\"At this point, 2023 sounds generous.\" src=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_small/0/8273/3453182-9067400311-Fq3tRS1aYAIXn-j.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3453182-9067400311-Fq3tRS1aYAIXn-j.jpg 2048w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_super/0/8273/3453182-9067400311-Fq3tRS1aYAIXn-j.jpg 960w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/0/8273/3453182-9067400311-Fq3tRS1aYAIXn-j.jpg 480w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_small/0/8273/3453182-9067400311-Fq3tRS1aYAIXn-j.jpg 320w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 320px) 100vw, 320px\" data-width=\"320\"></a><figcaption>At this point, 2023 sounds generous.</figcaption></figure><p data-right-indent=\"0\" style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">After a negative reaction to what was shown during Sony's State of Play, <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/suicide-squad-kill-the-justice-league/3030-80097/\">Suicide Squad: Kill the Justice League</a> has been delayed AGAIN! What do you make of the game's current state? Is the new timetable doable? Join the discussion on the forums.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/starfield/3030-68921/forums/starfield-gets-a-release-date-september-6th-2023-1910224/\"><strong>Starfield Gets A Release Date (September 6th, 2023)</strong></a> (By: <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/profile/allthedinos/\">@allthedinos</a>)</p><p data-right-indent=\"0\" style=\"margin-left: 30px;\"><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/starfield/3030-68921/\">Starfield</a> has a release date! Based on what they have shown of the game thus far, does September 6th, 2023 sound realistic? Have you enjoyed what you have seen of the game thus far?</p><p><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/resident-evil-4/3030-86329/forums/re4-remake-is-about-three-weeks-away-1910197/\"><strong>RE4 Remake Is About Three Weeks Away</strong></a> (By: <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/profile/atheistpreacher/\">@atheistpreacher</a>)</p><figure data-align=\"right\" data-size=\"small\" data-img-src=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3453280-0442974598-Starf.jpg\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3453280\" data-ratio=\"0.635\" data-width=\"2000\" data-embed-type=\"image\" style=\"width: 2000px\"><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3453280-0442974598-Starf.jpg\"><img alt=\"In typical Bethesda form, they announced a release date alongside a delay.\" src=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_small/0/8273/3453280-0442974598-Starf.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3453280-0442974598-Starf.jpg 2000w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_super/0/8273/3453280-0442974598-Starf.jpg 960w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/0/8273/3453280-0442974598-Starf.jpg 480w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_small/0/8273/3453280-0442974598-Starf.jpg 320w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 320px) 100vw, 320px\" data-width=\"320\"></a><figcaption>In typical Bethesda form, they announced a release date alongside a delay.</figcaption></figure><p data-right-indent=\"0\" style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">The <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/resident-evil-4/3030-86329/\">Resident Evil 4</a> is coming out in about three weeks! CRAZY, RIGHT?! How many of you are excited to get your hands on it? What do you expect to see in it that hasn't been shown yet?</p><p><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/nintendo-switch/3045-157/forums/switch-lite-in-2023-is-it-worth-buying-1910204/\"><strong>Switch Lite In 2023 - Is It Worth Buying?</strong></a> (By: <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/profile/isomeri/\">@isomeri</a>)</p><p data-right-indent=\"0\" style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">The Switch Lite is constantly on sale, but is it a good value proposition at this point? What are the pitfalls and benefits of jumping into the Switch ecosystem with the Lite model?</p><p><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/daydream-forgotten-sorrow/3030-86581/forums/daydream-prologue-available-now-1910203/\"><strong>Daydream: Prologue Available Now</strong></a> (By: <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/profile/keoskey/\">@keoskey</a>)</p><p data-right-indent=\"0\" style=\"margin-left: 30px;\"><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/daydream-forgotten-sorrow/3030-86581/\">Daydream: Forgotten Sorrow</a> recently got a a demo/Prologue that lets you play the first act on Steam! Have any of you given the prologue a try? If so, join the community discussion about it and share if you are excited to get your hands on the whole thing.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/forums/general-discussion-30/your-thoughts-on-the-current-state-of-the-video-ga-1910179/\"><strong>Your Thoughts On The Current State Of The Video Game Industry? (As Of March 5th, 2023)</strong></a> (By: <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/profile/gtxforza/\">@gtxforza</a>)</p><figure data-align=\"right\" data-size=\"small\" data-img-src=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3453281-9122857953-Fq0OOE8aMAAHmrp.jpg\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3453281\" data-ratio=\"0.93008130081301\" data-width=\"615\" data-embed-type=\"image\" style=\"width: 615px\"><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3453281-9122857953-Fq0OOE8aMAAHmrp.jpg\"><img alt=\"I Tweeted this poll and have not been banned on Twitter. Color me surprised!\" src=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_small/0/8273/3453281-9122857953-Fq0OOE8aMAAHmrp.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3453281-9122857953-Fq0OOE8aMAAHmrp.jpg 615w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/0/8273/3453281-9122857953-Fq0OOE8aMAAHmrp.jpg 480w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_small/0/8273/3453281-9122857953-Fq0OOE8aMAAHmrp.jpg 320w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 320px) 100vw, 320px\" data-width=\"320\"></a><figcaption>I Tweeted this poll and have not been banned on Twitter. Color me surprised!</figcaption></figure><p data-right-indent=\"0\" style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">A lot's going on in the games industry, so, what are your thoughts about the direction the industry is going right now? Are there games coming out you are excited about? Thoughts about recent gaming events like the closure or layoffs hitting some studios or the big merger looming in the background?</p><p><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/cities-skylines-ii/3030-88679/forums/cities-skylines-ii-achievements-drop-early-officia-1910196/\"><strong>Cities: Skylines II Achievements Drop Early; Officially Confirmed For 2023 on PC and Consoles</strong></a> (By: <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/profile/keoskey/\">@keoskey</a>)</p><p data-right-indent=\"0\" style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">The PC and console versions of <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/cities-skylines-ii/3030-88679/\">Cities: Skylines II</a> are now officially confirmed for this year! Is anyone excited to get your hands on this game? For those that played the original, what's on your wishlist?</p><p><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/forums/general-discussion-30/which-new-verb-is-better-description-in-message-1910265/\"><strong>Which New Verb Is Better? (Description In Message)</strong></a> (By: <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/profile/axl159/\">@axl159</a>)</p><p data-right-indent=\"0\" style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">I have nothing to add other than to recommend you check out the poll explanation to the right and vote your conscience. Godspeed everyone.</p><h2>Lists</h2><p><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/profile/mento/lists/the-legend-of-the-zeldersatz/374253/\"><strong>The Legend of the Zeldersatz</strong></a> (By: <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/profile/mento/\">@mento</a>)</p><figure data-align=\"right\" data-size=\"small\" data-img-src=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3453279-5697341889-Fq0P4u1aMAITGHv.jpg\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3453279\" data-ratio=\"0.42867924528302\" data-width=\"1325\" data-embed-type=\"image\" style=\"width: 1325px\"><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3453279-5697341889-Fq0P4u1aMAITGHv.jpg\"><img alt=\"Prepare for a new list where Mento is in peak form!\" src=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_small/0/8273/3453279-5697341889-Fq0P4u1aMAITGHv.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3453279-5697341889-Fq0P4u1aMAITGHv.jpg 1325w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_super/0/8273/3453279-5697341889-Fq0P4u1aMAITGHv.jpg 960w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/0/8273/3453279-5697341889-Fq0P4u1aMAITGHv.jpg 480w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_small/0/8273/3453279-5697341889-Fq0P4u1aMAITGHv.jpg 320w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 320px) 100vw, 320px\" data-width=\"320\"></a><figcaption>Prepare for a new list where Mento is in peak form!</figcaption></figure><p data-right-indent=\"0\" style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">The video game industry has seen its fair share of <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/the-legend-of-zelda/3025-9/\">The Legend of Zelda</a> clones or Zelda-likes throughout history. This week, moderator Mento annotated the most notable classic and modern games to pull inspiration from Zelda and boiled them into a sentence!</p><p><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/profile/thefakepsychic/lists/tfps-top-10-games-of-2022/374252/\"><strong>TFP's Top 10 Games of 2022</strong></a> (By: <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/profile/thefakepsychic/\">@thefakepsychic</a>)</p><p data-right-indent=\"0\" style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">It took some time, but TheFakePsychic finally got around to making a 2022 GOTY list on Giant Bomb! Give it a read and see which games made their last year in terms of gaming and always feel free to make your own list if you haven't already.</p><figure data-align=\"right\" data-size=\"small\" data-img-src=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3453180-8105711209-FqvTTi3aMAEQgLQ.png\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3453180\" data-ratio=\"0.7455919395466\" data-width=\"794\" data-embed-type=\"image\" style=\"width: 794px\"><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3453180-8105711209-FqvTTi3aMAEQgLQ.png\"><img alt=\"Every season is GOTY season, if you ask me.\" src=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_small/0/8273/3453180-8105711209-FqvTTi3aMAEQgLQ.png\" srcset=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3453180-8105711209-FqvTTi3aMAEQgLQ.png 794w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/0/8273/3453180-8105711209-FqvTTi3aMAEQgLQ.png 480w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_small/0/8273/3453180-8105711209-FqvTTi3aMAEQgLQ.png 320w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 320px) 100vw, 320px\" data-width=\"320\"></a><figcaption>Every season is GOTY season, if you ask me.</figcaption></figure><p><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/profile/boosturook/lists/games-where-you-break-out-of-prisonjail/374249/\"><strong>Games Where You Break-Out of Prison/Jail</strong></a> (By: <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/profile/boosturook/\">@boosturook</a>)</p><p data-right-indent=\"0\" style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">BoosTurook is working on a fun list on Giant Bomb that needs YOUR HELP! They want to make the most definitive listing of \"Games Where You Break-Out of Prison/Jail!\" Here's their first draft, and if you have suggestions, click the link.</p><h2>User Reviews</h2><figure data-align=\"right\" data-size=\"small\" data-img-src=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3453274-1224148842-Fq8zFezaUAAuizz.jpg\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3453274\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-width=\"1280\" data-embed-type=\"image\" style=\"width: 1280px\"><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3453274-1224148842-Fq8zFezaUAAuizz.jpg\"><img alt=\"I guess I'm not at all surprised everyone is still talking about this game.\" src=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_small/0/8273/3453274-1224148842-Fq8zFezaUAAuizz.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3453274-1224148842-Fq8zFezaUAAuizz.jpg 1280w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_super/0/8273/3453274-1224148842-Fq8zFezaUAAuizz.jpg 960w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/0/8273/3453274-1224148842-Fq8zFezaUAAuizz.jpg 480w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_small/0/8273/3453274-1224148842-Fq8zFezaUAAuizz.jpg 320w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 320px) 100vw, 320px\" data-width=\"320\"></a><figcaption>I guess I'm not at all surprised everyone is still talking about this game.</figcaption></figure><p data-right-indent=\"0\" style=\"margin-left: 30px;\"><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/profile/blakers87/\">@blakers87</a>'s <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/cyberpunk-2077/3030-38456/user-reviews/2200-32231/\"><strong>Cyberpunk 2077</strong></a> review talks about the game's current state, what they think is its path forward, and why they ended up loving its quieter moments more than anything else.</p><h2>Wiki Of The Week</h2><p><strong><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/street-fighter-duel/3030-84502/\">Street Fighter Duel</a></strong></p><figure data-align=\"right\" data-size=\"small\" data-img-src=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3453265-7853736163-Fq82OjmagAIgwQO.jpg\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3453265\" data-ratio=\"0.56276445698166\" data-width=\"709\" data-embed-type=\"image\" style=\"width: 709px\"><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3453265-7853736163-Fq82OjmagAIgwQO.jpg\"><img alt=\"No Caption Provided\" src=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_small/0/8273/3453265-7853736163-Fq82OjmagAIgwQO.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3453265-7853736163-Fq82OjmagAIgwQO.jpg 709w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/0/8273/3453265-7853736163-Fq82OjmagAIgwQO.jpg 480w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_small/0/8273/3453265-7853736163-Fq82OjmagAIgwQO.jpg 320w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 320px) 100vw, 320px\" data-width=\"320\"></a></figure><p data-right-indent=\"0\" style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">Thanks to some INCREDIBLE editing work by <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/profile/daavpuke/\">@daavpuke</a>, the Street Fighter Duel wiki page is the Wiki Page of the Week! Learn all there is to know about the Street Fighter gacha game and how it works!</p>"),
            imageUrl = "https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/screen_medium/0/1992/3453312-untitled-1.png",
            source = Source.GiantBomb,
            content = null,
            thumbnailUrl = null,
            sourceLinkUrl = "content",
